        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          The frame is frozen. What should I do?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          Use RELOAD to refresh only the embedded game. This avoids reloading the full site.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Is this the official game website?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          No. FunClicker.click is an independent guide and play page.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Can I report broken content or legal issues?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          Yes. Use our Contact or DMCA page and include the exact URL and details.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Does the site require an account?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          No account is required to open and play the embedded game.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Why are ads shown on this site?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          Ads support hosting and content maintenance. See our Privacy and Cookie Policy for details.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Can I disable cookies?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 italic">
          Yes. You can change cookie settings in your browser, but some features may stop working.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="py-6 group cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="font-black text-lg uppercase flex justify-between items-center list-none">
          Is any personal information required to play?
          <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">‚ñº</span>
        </summary>
